flowchart TD
    FIT["`Model overfits (train >> val score)`"] --> Q{What kind of model?}
    Q -->|Linear / logistic regression| REG[Add regularization penalty]
    Q -->|Tree-based| TREE["max_depth, min_samples_leaf, n_estimators limits"]
    Q -->|Neural network| NN["Dropout, weight decay, batch norm"]

    REG --> L1["`L1 / Lasso → sparse weights (feature selection)`"]
    REG --> L2["`L2 / Ridge → small weights (keeps all features)`"]
    REG --> EN["`Elastic Net → both penalties (correlated features)`"]

    L1 & L2 & EN --> CV["`Use cross-validation to choose λ (alpha)`"]
    CV --> PLOT["`Plot val score vs log(α) Pick peak`"]
